      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KAREN STRATUS (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (30.37) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here sound including four wins. Has won three of four starts from this draw. Should be very hard to beat this time. GOOD ODDS KEONA (1) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at Gosford over 515m behind Speedy Zipper (31.14) in a Grade 5. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Shapes as one to consider. ZIPPING GRESSIER (8) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.95 beating Zipping Daly. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Sure to measure up. HOOKED ON JOY (4) boasts a solid strike-rate from this box.",
